ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectAuditor General of Canada - Public Service Alliance of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving the ENTRY by Auditor General of Canada into a COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the Public Service Alliance of Canada of Canada that covers all employees in the Audit Services Group bargaining unit for the period beginning on October 1, 2023 and ending on September 30, 2025.
